{"tid":1322182,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"戒嚴係正苦放風 想做輿論等啲人怪責遊行示威人士","createTime":"2019-07-16T01:09:40.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-16T14:49:26.000Z","uid":41870,"like":14,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"e8cbf312493ab7c80b9a2126870fb0ddd6f77fc6","tid":1322182,"uid":41870,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-16T01:09:40.000Z","msg":"呢點兩點睇：<br />\n1. 會令啲錢字行頭既深藍港豬怪示威者阻佢地搵食<br />\n2. 令商家佬驚 戒嚴一日搵少幾多個億<br />\n<br />\n但係<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">唔撚洗驚佢</span><br />\n<br />\n而家打緊美中貿易戰，香港係唯一一個係中國國際化啲既金融市場，佢一戒嚴就即係話拎香港黎攬炒！風險極大！一旦貿易戰輸左中共就玩完！唔好忘記已經好多外資撤左資，搬左廠去越南！<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n <br />\n唔洗驚唔好亂陣腳<br />\n誰怕誰<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n香港人，加油！今鋪打大佬<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1e47bbb5c9d1c0c88428865048b8e2d7d328fc55","tid":1322182,"uid":41870,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-16T01:16:18.000Z","msg":"推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"df226cca838d703657629f5016210a63877872b9","tid":1322182,"uid":9824,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-16T01:20:24.000Z","msg":"<pre><code data-type=\"\">有人冒警！\n你扮警察\n涉嫌冒警及傷人\n涉嫌藏有攻擊性武器\n我地行使公民逮捕權</code></pre>"},{"pid":"ad5522ba42ed7452dbb5805427511b0ae608a110","tid":1322182,"uid":16628,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-16T14:49:26.000Z","msg":"幫推"}]}